Syntax: kill <creature>
Syntax: toggle kill

A good way to start a fight.  You will be unable to attack certain
creatures (immortals, deities, etc.)

The kill toggle will let you select whether you will continnue to attack
mortally wounded creatures or whether you will stop fighting once they
have reached mortally wounded.

See Also: TOGGLE, HIT, ENGAGE, ASSIST
Related Topics: COMBAT
